{
  "stem": "26142.17",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- but he didn't have any gauze.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They didn't have any gauze.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The only thing they had was-- you know what crepe paper is?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, those paper-- Crepe paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, that's what he had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he tied it-- tied it up and put me-- put me in the bed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, the untying and the tying-- the untying was worse later on, when he rebandaged this. because there was no gas or an aspirin, nothing he could give me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I stayed in-- in this hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I have to tell this story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Next to me, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- the-- the-- the bed was two.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like, three high, two wide.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Next to me in the bed was a French general.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a lot of Frenchmen, by the way, in this-- in this camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this French general had one foot amputated, and he was supposed to have the other foot amputated, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't know that that general, that French general, he spoke perfect German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't know-- at that time, I didn't know the German map.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't know where-- I knew we were close to Nuremberg, but I didn't know where it-- where it was and how close it is to the relation to the-- to the-- to the war front, the-- the war front.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember this general, one-- one day, he talked to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, the war is going to end in a week or two.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said, you will live to see the end of it but I-- I-- I won't.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I have to tell this story about him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This general-- there was a lot of Frenchmen in that revier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They-- they were talking in French.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
